          <p>Hack The Media is the gateway between you and the top tech and media talent on the planet. Whether you come to network, promote brand awareness, or get feedback on a product or API, we’ll help you connect with the right people who help you and your business.</p>
          <br>

          <p><b><i>Once you know how to code, you can build any application you like - a world of possibilities opens up to you. And I'm here to tell you, that anyone can do it, you don't need to be a maths wizz or computer nerd to be a coder. And it's fun! -- Pete Argent, Director, Coder Factory</i></b></p>
          <br>

